  FILTER ( LANG( ?profLabel ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?profLabel ) , 'politician' ) || CONTAINS( LCASE( ?profLabel ) , 'diplomat' ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>

  fb:m.015fr fb:location.country.form_of_government ?form .
